summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A BABY TREND EASY RIDE 5 TRAVEL SYSTEM  SAFETY SEAT, MODEL NUMBER: TS40971. THE SEAT WAS MANUFACTURED ON APRIL 15, 2015.
